For new fans: 
(in age order)

Scoups(Seungcheol): baggy jeans, grey button up over white shirt, yellowish beanie.

Jeonghan: All beige outfit, arm sling
Joshua: Black basketball shorts, white shirt, blue button up overtop
Jun(Junhui): Gren jeans with black side panels at bottom, dark grey tshirt with writing on it
Hoshi(Soonyoung): Camo pants, plaid button up shirt
Wonwoo: Beige pants, cream tshirt
Woozi(Jihoon): All black outfit, black shorts, black tshirt
DK(Dokyeom/Seokmin): Beige shorts, grey tshirt with the number '955' on front
Mingyu: All black outfit, black hoodie, black shorts, black glasses
The8(Minghao): Jeans, green button up shirt tucked in, pink hair
Seungkwan: Grey shirts, cream shirt with blue heart, blue hair
Vernon(Hansol): Black pants (jeans?), grey tshirt
Dino(Chan): Cream pants and shirt, grey zipup hoodie on top.

Scoups is the leader
Units are: 
Hiphop unit: Scoups, Wonwoo, Mingyu, Vernon
Performnce Unit: Hoshi,Jun, The8, Dino
Vocal Unit: Joshua, Jeonghan, Woozi, Dokyeom, Seungkwan

Enjoy!

author: @ScarletCloud
text:
I've just noticed in this choreo video the beautiful, creative (and kinda meaningful?) transition in 2:08. 

Jun's singing in the middle, next is Dino so he moves forward to the center. Then, in just a few seconds, Mingyu, Wonu and Vernon reagroup with Coups. Meanwhile, JeongHan, Joshua and Kwan run to reagroup with Woozi and DK. Vocal unit and hip hop unit moves in spiral during Mingyu and Seungkwan parts, and the center is being fullfilled with the performance unit having their own moves.

Edit: after seeing it again, more than spiral, it remind me more of the typical representation of the day, where sun and moon are moving to the same direction, opposite positioned, and Earth is in the middle.

MAGIC. /chef kiss
